DecisionTreeNode - Class in edu.jhu.nick.cs335.hw4.tree
Class that represents a Decision Tree Node and in turn, an entire Decision Tree Each Decision Tree Node contains a attribute value which is either the resulting classification or the current node's attribute, depending on whether this node is a leaf or not Each Node also contains a Map of Strings to other child nodes - The strings represent values that the root attribute could take mapped to the subtree associated with that action
